Web application deployment choices
1. Vercel (fast with Github integrations), great option for POC iteration
2. Elastic Container Service (lower cost and configurable by Terraform, need more leg work), great option for productionize the POC with known scaling trend
3. Digital Oceans app service (lower cost than Vercel but hihger cost than ECS, without Github integrations), happy medium option.

Web application types
1. SPA (Single Page Application based on Create React App), can be set up in S3, distributed with CloudFront
2. Next.js has more page rendering and data fetching models, improving client side page loading performance;  has dynmic routing to optimize devex
